<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَسَتْرُهُمَا لِمَحَلِّ فَرْضٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَإِمْكَانُ مَشْيٍ بِهِمَا عُرْفًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَثُبُوتُهُمَا بِنَفْسِهِمَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَإِبَاحَتُهُمَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَطَهَارَةُ عَيْنِهِمَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَعَدَمُ وَصْفِهِمَا البَشَرَةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَيَمْسَحُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- مُقِيمٌ، وَعَاصٍ بِسَفَرِهِ - مِنْ حَدَثٍ بَعْدَ لُبْسٍ -: يَوْمًا وَلَيْلَةً.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمُسَافِرٌ سَفَرَ قَصْرٍ لَمْ يَعْصِ بِهِ:</span> ثَلَاثَةً بِلَيَالِيهِنَّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَلَوْ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- مَسَحَ فِي سَفَرٍ ثُمَّ أَقَامَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- أَوْ فِي حَضَرٍ ثُمَّ سَافَرَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- أَوْ شَكَّ فِي ابْتِدَاءِ المَسْحِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَمْ يَزِدْ عَلَى مَسْحِ مُقِيمٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجُوزُ المَسْحُ عَلَى جَبِيرَةٍ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> إِنْ كَانَ وَضَعَهَا عَلَى طَهَارَةٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>